# Member Management Dashboard for NBA Sports Club
## Detailed Flow Chart Representation

```plaintext
+----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
|                                       Functional Requirements                                      |
+----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| - User Authentication (JWT, OAuth2.0, Role-Based Access Control)                                  |
| - Member Management: View, Add, Update, Delete (CRUD Operations)                                  |
| - Membership Payments: Subscription Plans, Invoicing, Payment Status Tracking                    |
| - Member Profiles: Personal Details, Photos, Preferences                                          |
| - Game/Events Bookings: Register Members for Events, Availability Management                      |
| - Notifications: Email, SMS, Push Notifications for Game Updates and Deadlines                   |
| - Analytics and Reports Dashboard: Membership Statistics, Event Participation Insights            |
+----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+

                         Glossary: React/Next.js + Node.js or .NET Core + PostgreSQL

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
START OF ARCHITECTURE FLOW CHART

(User Layer)
+---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| User Interaction                                                                                 |
| - Access Web UI via browser                                                                      |
| - Authenticate/Login                                                                              |
| - Interact with Dashboard: View Members, Payments, and Notifications                             |
+---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
                                    |
                                    v
                         Frontend Communication Layer
                         +---------------------------------------------------------------+
                         |                   Frontend Framework (React/Next.js)          |
                         +---------------------------------------------------------------+
                         | - React Components for User Interface:                       |
                         |    - Login Form, Member Details Pages, Event Registration    |
                         |    - Forms for CRUD Operations                               |
                         |    - Dashboards, Notifications, Analytics Widgets.           |
                         | - Integration with GraphQL/REST for API Interaction           |
                         | - Localization for Multi-language Support (if required)      |
                         +---------------------------------------------------------------+
                                    |
                                    v
--------------------------
+ Backend Communication +
--------------------------            Frontend initiates an API request through:
                                     - RESTful Endpoints (e.g., /members, /payments)
                                     - WebSockets for Real-Time Updates (e.g., Notifications)

-----------------------------------------------------------
(Backend Server Logic via Node.js or .NET Core)
+------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
|              Backend API Gateway: Node.js Express (Alt: ASP.NET Web API)                            |
|                                                                                                      |
| - Auth Module: JWT Generation, Token Refresh Endpoint                                                |
| - Controllers/Endpoints Layer (REST or GraphQL via Apollo Server)                                    |
|   - `/auth/login` - Authenticate and issue token                                                    |
|   - `/members/`   - Member CRUD endpoints with pagination                                            |
|   - `/payments/`  - Create/view/validate billing transactions                                        |
|   - `/games/`     - Member signups or registration for events                                        |
| - Services Layer:                                                                                   |
|   - Business Logic (Validation of User Role, Permission Checks)                                     |
|   - Server-Side Validation for Form Inputs (e.g., Input Sanitization)                               |
|   - Dependency Injection for Service Coupling (e.g., Payments, Members Database)                    |
| - Technologies:                                                                                     |
|   - Node.js: Core Backend Server                                                                    |
|   - Optional: .NET Core Web API Service                                                             |
+------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
                                    |
                                    v
--------------------
+ Database Layer +
--------------------        POSTGRESQL (Primary SQL Database):
                           - Data Access Layer Libraries:
                           - Node.js: Use Sequelize or TypeORM (ORM),
                           AspTables diagram
